snippet.title: Crispy Pro
snippet.description:
Hello there, my name is Crispy and welcome to the channel!

Much like my life, this channel is all about my favorite show in the universe 'Doctor Who'. 

I'll give you theories, discussions, reactions, interviews, parodies, music videos, and about everything in between! 

So go on, subscribe for some of the best content in the Whoniverse
